(135, 1, '2014-09-08 11:11:00', '2014-09-08 11:11:00', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-137 alignleft\" style=\"float: left; margin-right: 10px;\" src=\"http://dtechsystem.net/dev/wp-content/uploads/indian_fawadpix_02.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"259\" height=\"194\" />Actor Fawad Khan is set to become the latest Indian heartthrob. The Pakistani tele-serial ´ZindagiGulzar Hai´, airing on Zindagi channel has already caught the attention of viewers in India and Fawad Khan has rapidly acquired a huge fan following, particularly among the youth. He is scheduled to make his Bollywood debut with ´Khoobsurat´, co-starring SonamKapoor. The film is a remake of the Rekha hit with the same name. The film releases on September 19th across India. Fawad plays a sophisticated Rajput prince in the film who falls in love with the vivacious Sonam Kapoor.</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Fawad Khan is enjoying his second innings as a star, having first rocked Pakistan as a rock star with his band Entity Paradigm in the early 2000s. He turned actor in 2007 and made waves with his portrayal of a singer-turned-jihadi in the blockbuster film ´Khuda Kay Liye´. His television serials like the megahits ´Dastaan´ and ´Humsafar´ and telefilm ´Behad´ brought him several thousand more fans, making him a super star in Pakistan.</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Considering the impact his portrayal of the extrovert and chauvinistic ZaroonJunaid in ´ZindagiGulzar Hai´ has had on Indian audiences, it can be safely assumed that this Pakistani actor is here to say.</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Fawad Khan spent a good part of his childhood in UAE, Greece and UK as the family travelled with his father who worked for a pharmaceutical firm. In 1992 the family moved back to Lahore but by then Fawad Khan had acquired a ´Yankee accent´ as he puts it. It took him a long time to ditch the accent. Fawad Khan was diagnosed with severe diabetes at the age of 17 and it says a lot for his focus, grit and determination that he overcome the disease to become a rock star and a superstar in Pakistan. And now he is set to conquer hearts in India.</p>', 'The New Khan in Bollywood', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'the-new-khan-in-bollywood', '', '', '2018-08-02 09:04:48', '2018-08-02 09:04:48', '', 0, 'http://dtechsystem.net/dev/?p=135', 0, 'post', '', 0),
