(371, 1, '2014-05-16 11:03:20', '2014-05-16 11:03:20', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Population: <strong>742,737</strong> and happens to be the 165th nation of the world in terms of population.</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">No official data on the status of demography in Bhutan.</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngalops and Sharchopsconstitue main population called the Western and Eastern Bhutanese. The Lhotshampa, meaning \"Southern Bhutanese\' happen to be a heterogeneous group comprising of mostly Nepali origin people. It was claimed they constituted 45% of the population in 1988 censusand included even the migrant Nepalis to the region. There is also an unofficial data that puts the muslim population in the country to about 5% but official it is said to be less than 1%.</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Main religions: Buddhism (state religion), Hinduism</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Main minority groups: Nepali-speakers (35%), indigenous and others (15%)</p>', 'Bhutan', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'bhutan', '', '', '2018-08-03 10:13:58', '2018-08-03 10:13:58', '', 0, 'http://dtechsystem.net/dev/?p=371', 0, 'post', '', 0);
